humbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F111220_1d68d67320de5dbb1db5d434d60a1a24.jpg&h=cd94e967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓上班人根本唔撚識 一早畀咗router型號喺到話線問題底板問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無底板L知佢關唔關底板lan事呀,一定剩係router問題!?而家線都有問題啦屌<br />\n<br />\n你未又係柒</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">下面係指砌機底板，NB除外。</span><br />\n底板GB lan已經標準配置。<br />\n底板用100mb lan反而難搵。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪又係我問佢先post config , 之前佢都無講 , 近年d底板就係 , 鬼知佢部機新定舊"},{"pid":"86e4a16306a2df6aa30bf32fafe9436f8d77f67c","tid":357492,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"我都係用緊樓主用一router, 300M但出100M,<br />\n但直插電腦可以300M, <br />\n樓主直插出唔到300M<br />\n換個gigabit lan router 可能都唔得,"},{"pid":"3784b1d90b791c0413241ab24048e84705e7da87","tid":357492,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係用緊樓主用一router, 300M但出100M,<br />\n但直插電腦可以300M, <br />\n樓主直插出唔到300M<br />\n換個gigabit lan router 可能都唔得,</blockquote><br />\n我條LAN線4芯 你條係咪8芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9690b41f2215590fb5adb066334802cc0a2c84ec","tid":357492,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係用緊樓主用一router, 300M但出100M,<br />\n但直插電腦可以300M, <br />\n樓主直插出唔到300M<br />\n換個gigabit lan router 可能都唔得,</blockquote><br />\n我條LAN線4芯 你條係咪8芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋gigabit lan router有冇推介"},{"pid":"3729f3e5ca057e5ab70eceb94730574355e0aa81","tid":357492,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/111220_1d68d67320de5dbb1db5d434d60a1a24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F111220_1d68d67320de5dbb1db5d434d60a1a24.jpg&h=cd94e967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓上班人根本唔撚識 一早畀咗router型號喺到話線問題底板問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無底板L知佢關唔關底板lan事呀,一定剩係router問題!?而家線都有問題啦屌<br />\n<br />\n你未又係柒</blockquote><br />\n嗱 底板lan / chipset / router cable 同埋modem 4樣嘢要support gigabit lan先行到gigabit有邊個唔識講？<br />\n<br />\n樓主畀咗router型號但你當咗router行到200MB 用你個解難嘅步驟 就算換完線都只會繼續R頭點解都係得100MB<br />\n<br />\n解難就應該見一個問題就即刻拆嘅 畀咗router型號都spot唔到個問題唔係唔識？<br />\n<br />\n從更實際嘅方向去諗 買router實送線 線嘅問題一定擺喺router之後先處理"},{"pid":"b0bc99b1a15d2f2fc0df6a7dd463c3f5e1d3c511","tid":357492,"uid":15243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"總之係得四個可能性<br />\n1.router問題<br />\n2.電腦底板問題 太舊 <br />\n3.Lan要CAT5 6 最好當然用7<br />\n4.你個plan冇200Mbps速度"}]}